"'''The Dethronement of Power'''" is the title of the literary review of ''[[The Two Towers]]'' and ''[[The Return of the King]]''. It was written by [[C.S. Lewis]] and originally published in ''Time and Tide'' on [[22 October]] [[1955]] (p. 1373). It has since been reprinted in ''[[Tolkien and the Critics]]''.
